	<h1>ADOPT</h1>
    <h2>The Best Things In Life Are Resqued. And Even Better When You Take Them Home</h2>
    <h3>Adopting An Animal And Bringing Home A New Family Member Is Truly A Wonderful Feeling.<br>However, The First Question You Need To Ask is: <big>Are You Ready To Adopt A Pet?</big></h3>
    
    <br>
    <h2><b><big>Here Are Few Steps To Adopt A Pet From PetPash:</big></b></h2><br>
    <dl>
    <big><dt><h3 style="font-size:25px"><b>....Be Absoutely 100% Sure You Want To Adopt....</b></big></h3><span></span></dt>
        <dd>Read up. Talk To People. Be Certain. You Take Weeks, If Not Months, To Evaluate Which Vehicle You Buy.<br>In This Case It's A Live Animal, Who Eats, Sleeps, Breathes And FEELS. Take Your Time To Be Sure You Are Ready To Adopt!!</span></dd>
    <big><dt><h3 style="font-size:25px"><b>....Fill Up PetPash Adoption Application....</b></h3><span></span></dt></big>
    <dd>Take Your Time To Fill This One. Be Honest With Your Replies. We're Seasoned Adoption Filtering Agents. We Can Sniff And Detect Discrepancies Like Hounds.</dd> <br><br>
